Package org.pikater.web.vaadin.gui.server.components.popups.dialogs

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DialogCommons.IDialogComponent  
    DialogCommons.IDialogResultHandler
    Interface providing methods for handling dialog button clicks.
    DialogCommons.IDialogResultPreparer
    Interface providing validation and pre-processing methods to dialog buttons.
    DialogCommons.IDialogResultValidator
    Interface providing validation methods to dialog buttons.
    ProgressDialog.IProgressDialogResultHandler
    Classes implementing this object are supposed to handle the underlying tracked task's progress, whether successful or not.
    ProgressDialog.IProgressDialogTaskHandler
    Classes implementing this object are supposed to manage the underlying tracked task.
    ProgressDialog.IProgressDialogTaskResult
    A base interface for objects that hold the underlying task's results.

    A utility class to implement specialized dialogs for a particular use.
